        <sponsor name-id="S001162">Ms. Schwartz</sponsor> (for herself, <cosponsor name-id="C001038">Mr. Crowley</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="G000564">Mr. Gibson</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="K000210">Mr. King of New York</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="N000015">Mr. Neal</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was referred to the <committee-name committee-id="HWM00">Committee on Ways and Means</committee-name>
